title: Libya’s ‘Masked Men’ Hunt Human Smugglers
text:
ZUWARA, Libya—For decades this town on Libya’s Mediterranean coast has been a hub for trafficking between Africa and Europe. One morning in late August, Zuwara awoke to a tragedy involving the local criminals’ latest cargo: humans.
